headline: Stock Market Today: Dow Edges Up As Tesla Jumps Near Buy Point, Apple Lags (Live Coverage)
summary: Stock Market Today: The Dow Jones index rose Monday but Apple stock lagged. Tesla raced higher, nearing a buy point.

headline: 1 Dow Jones Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 We Brush Off
summary: The Dow Jones (^DJI) is made up of 30 of the most established and influential companies in the market. But even blue-chip stocks can struggle - some are dealing with slowing growth, outdated business models, or increasing competition.
